==English==
===Noun===
'''acidophile''' ({{plural}} acidophiles)
# an [[organism]] that [[live]]s and [[thrive]]s under [[acidic]] [[condition]]s; a form of [[extremophile]]
# a [[plant]] that will thrive in relatively acid [[soil]]

